text: Hagen im Bremischen is a municipality in Cuxhaven, in Lower Saxony, Germany. It is about 20 km south of Bremerhaven, and 35 km northwest of Bremen. Hagen was the seat of the former Samtgemeinde ("collective municipality") Hagen. == References == Category:Cuxhaven (district)
title: Hagen im Bremischen
